---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<p class="footer__tagline">Not a fan blog — just someone learning Taylor Swift lore one song at a time.</p>
	<p class="footer__copy">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Boyfriend&apos;s Guide. Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>.</p>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.5em 1.25em 3em;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(var(--gray-light), 0.35));
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.footer__tagline {
		margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
		max-width: 28rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.footer__copy {
		margin: 0;
	}

	footer a {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
</style>
